      "text": "MarketSelector\nuseMarketCatalog()\n/api/catalog?venue=hl\n  ↓\nopenVenueFeed() — SSE\n/api/feed → markPx\n(indexer-fronted\nHyperliquid catalog)", "originalText": "MarketSelector\nuseMarketCatalog()\n/api/catalog?venue=hl\n  ↓\nopenVenueFeed() — SSE\n/api/feed → markPx\n(indexer-fronted\nHyperliquid catalog)",
