    {
      "type": "text", "id": "oct2", "x": 634, "y": 592, "width": 252, "height": 216,
      "text": "treasury::open_account\n (AdminCap, eval fee)\n  ↓\nuser_account::create_account\n mints AccountCap → trader\n eval fee → eval_funds_balance\nemits AccountCreated", "originalText": "treasury::open_account\n (AdminCap, eval fee)\n  ↓\nuser_account::create_account\n mints AccountCap → trader\n eval fee → eval_funds_balance\nemits AccountCreated",
