    {
      "type": "text", "id": "oct6", "x": 1914, "y": 592, "width": 252, "height": 216,
      "text": "user_account::\n pass_evaluation()\n fail_evaluation()\n (ExecutorCap)\n  ↓\nstatus: Evaluating →\n Passed / Failed\n\n[v2 · executor-driven]", "originalText": "user_account::\n pass_evaluation()\n fail_evaluation()\n (ExecutorCap)\n  ↓\nstatus: Evaluating →\n Passed / Failed\n\n[v2 · executor-driven]",
