      "text": "user_account::promote\n (AdminCap → next tier)\n  ↓\nvault_reserve::\n withdraw_for_trading()\n→ real LP capital allocated\n→ funded trading begins", "originalText": "user_account::promote\n (AdminCap → next tier)\n  ↓\nvault_reserve::\n withdraw_for_trading()\n→ real LP capital allocated\n→ funded trading begins",
