      "text": "VaultRegistry  (vault_reserve)\nLP shares · NAV · Suilend yield\nprovide() / redeem()\nwithdraw_for_trading / return_from_trading\ndraw_for_lending / return_from_lending", "originalText": "VaultRegistry  (vault_reserve)\nLP shares · NAV · Suilend yield\nprovide() / redeem()\nwithdraw_for_trading / return_from_trading\ndraw_for_lending / return_from_lending",
