      "text": "Treasury  (treasury)\n3 USDC pools: fees · eval · payout\ncollect_eval_fee · fund_payouts\naccrue_payout · claim\n(pull-payment + timelocked addresses)", "originalText": "Treasury  (treasury)\n3 USDC pools: fees · eval · payout\ncollect_eval_fee · fund_payouts\naccrue_payout · claim\n(pull-payment + timelocked addresses)",
