    {
      "type": "text", "id": "diverget", "x": 320, "y": 1172, "width": 2320, "height": 152,
      "text": "⚠  KNOWN DIVERGENCES FROM THE V2 SPEC  (contracts/sui/PRD.md)\n•  AccountCap is transferable (has store) — spec wants it soulbound / non-transferable (the trader's durable passport)\n•  Starter profit split seeded 80/20 — spec says 75/25\n•  Eval state is mutated in place via reactivate() / promote() — spec wants a fresh TradingAccount object per attempt\n•  First-payout eval-fee refund: NOT implemented      •  Multisig VaultCap gate on payouts: NOT implemented      •  On-chain evaluation time-limit: open question\n•  propfirm.move is still an empty stub", "originalText": "⚠  KNOWN DIVERGENCES FROM THE V2 SPEC  (contracts/sui/PRD.md)\n•  AccountCap is transferable (has store) — spec wants it soulbound / non-transferable (the trader's durable passport)\n•  Starter profit split seeded 80/20 — spec says 75/25\n•  Eval state is mutated in place via reactivate() / promote() — spec wants a fresh TradingAccount object per attempt\n•  First-payout eval-fee refund: NOT implemented      •  Multisig VaultCap gate on payouts: NOT implemented      •  On-chain evaluation time-limit: open question\n•  propfirm.move is still an empty stub",
      "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#92400e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 110003, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 110004, "isDeleted": false,
      "groupIds": [], "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": "diverge", "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
